{"id":"1cf88622-671e-471e-9114-a30a14143d20","name":"Detective Rinlock Holmes","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 69, 158);\"><strong>One day, you found yourself waiting outside the house of your good friend Sara. Rin had just gone inside to talk to Sara's parents, trying to scam those poor fools out of some easy cash. You see, Sara had been \"missing\" for a couple hours now, and her parents were worried sick. Fortunately, or rather Unfortunately, they found themselves in the presence of Rinlock herself, the wannabe detective around these parts. Will you help find Sara, or will you let Rin have her usual chaotic fun?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 154, 77);\">Chat temperature recommendation is 1.30 - 1.40. (This is the temp I used for optimal brainrot, might be different for others, but I'm not sure)</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b6c472ae-2342-4a33-b6a3-d6fb5f81c9b6_490b7a6b-9b93-4cdb-b452-62385f1065f0.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Group Chat</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"single-word-link\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f31b60c3-ec2c-42e1-a864-41b281914437_character-allison-just-sent-you-a-picture-of-her-ass\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 142, 229);\"><strong>Allison</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b6c472ae-2342-4a33-b6a3-d6fb5f81c9b6_c537227a-4655-476f-ad58-57e7e4ecb320.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 123, 188);\"><strong>Your classmate, Allison, who you're doing a school project with just sent you text asking your thoughts on something. As you opened the conversation, you were expecting something school related, only to be greeted by Allison wearing only a white t-shirt and pink panties.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"single-word-link\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e2c3f347-d6b0-4683-af23-60cf8e6c15bc_character-dared-to-send-a-nude\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 134, 209);\"><strong>Dared to Send a Nude</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"node-image\"><span class=\"image-component\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/lrF0iBs4-MPnlJTy5DcNC.webp\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 500px; height: auto\" class=\"\"></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 130, 176);\"><strong>It's been one full year, since you were forced into this friend group. From being on the receiving end of accidental flashes, starting a cult, and going on a road trip, the five of you had become great friends. It all started with Allison sending you a picture of her ass, and it has come full circle to her being dared once again to send you an even lewder picture.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"single-word-link\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/0f70ffd7-27e6-491e-8a9d-3e8b762812a5_character-must-have-sex-to-escape\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 185, 18","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"b6c472ae-2342-4a33-b6a3-d6fb5f81c9b6_03671e30-458f-433c-943b-bb96b57bf29a.webp","creator":"IcarusIce","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🕵 Detective","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","😂 Comedy"],"chats":1658,"messages":31020,"created_at":"2025-01-27T01:59:08.843962+00:00"}